{
  "schema_version": "1.1",
  "selection_method": "Whitelist journals using SCImago SJR 2024 quartiles as a quality proxy; use tiered topical gating for discipline/practice venues.",
  "notes": [
    "Tier A journals are core higher-education didactics / SoTL / assessment / online learning venues.",
    "Tier B includes discipline-anchored education journals (management education; OR/analytics education) and one practice-oriented analytics journal that requires stricter education-intent gating to avoid irrelevant results.",
    "OpenAlex source_id fields may be left null; the script should resolve them at runtime via OpenAlex source search and then cache resolved IDs in state.json to speed up later runs."
